      "description": "Vacuum arc melting with four remelts, homogenization at 1100°C for 2 h followed by water quenching, hot rolling at 1100°C with ~50% thickness reduction and finish rolling around 900°C followed by air cooling, and intercritical annealing at 700°C for 1 h followed by water quenching.",
